description:
I am an honest, trustworthy and caring guy. I like to go places and do things but I am missing someone do do them with .I am a gentleman. It’s in my nature to open the door or pull out the chair for the lady I am with. I enjoy being romantic and doing special things that let the woman I am with know she is special and how much I care. I am looking for someone who is genuine and true and likes to be held and cuddled when we are alone together or holding each other’s hands as we walk. I am looking for someone who will treat me like they want to be treated. I want someone who will communicate with me openly as a friend and a lover. I am a very affectionate person and I just want the same in return. I want to find someone to be my best friend and someone that is willing to merge her heart with mine to beat and love as one. I do not like this on line dating but this is apparently what we do in this time period. I am not into games or just hook ups.
I am looking for someone to meet over drinks or dinner face to face and eyes to eyes and find out about each other and see where it leads. Maybe I am wanting to much but I will not settle for less. None of us are perfect (me included). I just want to love and be loved. Are we the missing pieces to each other’s heart that are destined to be together?

name: Jeshua
description:
Soy Carismático, Alegre, Pro-activo, Soñador, Enamorado de la Vida, y un Luchador Incansable por Naturaleza… Pienso que para trascender en la vida, es importante la huella que dejas en la vida de otras personas, no importa quién seas, mucho menos tu posición económica, solo basta que puedas creer, para que puedas alcanzar cosas maravillosas, y ayudar a que otros puedan lograrlo. La actitud positiva, los sueños, el conocimiento y el buen humor son las ruedas sobre las que asiento mis días.

Me gustan las personas alegres, divergentes, soñadoras, emprendedoras, inquietas, que constantemente están buscando que cosas extraordinarias ocurran en sus vidas. Esas de humor inteligente y picaresco, que prestan atención a los pequeños detalles, que no temen ir por sus sueños y deseos, que apuestan al amor y están dispuestas a todo por ver satisfecho sus propósitos junto a ese amor. Me encantan las personas guerreras, esas que entienden que los días buenos te dan felicidad y los malos suman experiencias y te hacen más fuerte. Me gustas las personas que abrazan, que miman, que ríen, que lloran, que besan, que no temen a sus debilidades, que no temen hablar, que no temen sentir y mostrarse vivos ante la vida.

Me gusta, el cine, la gastronomía, la cocina, viajar, compartir miradas que se dejen sentir profundamente, caricias delicadas de matices cálidos que sepan transmitir, la desnudes de los cuerpos (en pareja), la inmensidad del mar, el frío, el abrigo siempre necesario en las montaña. jijijiji... Ya me puse intenso! jajajaja... Me gusta Europa en su máxima expresión, su naturaleza, la movida nocturna y cultural, las barbacoas en familia, estar en casa abrigados junto a tu amor; aunque ya tengo uno hermoso de 9 años que me aviva las ganas día a día y quien es mi compañero de aventuras (yo su sancho y el mi quijote). En definitiva, desde hace un tiempo mantengo mi copa vacía, esperando que algo intenso y extraordinario pueda llenarla! Y, justo entonces volveré a brindar... Te Espero! Gracias por leer, eso habla bien de ti. Se nota que me gusta hablar! Besos...

name: animalluvrmike
description:
My name is Mike, I am 51, single/divorced (5 yrs), I live in Myrtle Beach South Carolina. I'm originally from Boston area, with a 13 year detour to Oklahoma. I don't have any kids of my own, have 2 step-kids that are now full grown adults, as well as a teen step granddaughter. They may not be mine in blood but I love them like my own and if the right woman has children I would do the same for them. I am disabled/retired, I have a few medical issues like diabetes that has destroyed parts of me, but not the important stuff. I currently live with my mom who is disabled and in a wheelchair so I help her with whatever I can.

I am a down to earth, quite, and shy guy, until I get to know you then I will open up and can be social, funny, outgoing, spontaneous, playful. I am also a very sensitive, loving, emotional, caring, romantic, honest, patient, and forgiving to a fault kind of man. I am a giver I like to make people (especially my significant other) happy whenever I can. I am not the typical guy who just wants to get in your pants as soon as possible. I Like to get to know someone, become friends, possibly date and see how it goes, if things are great then I would definitely be up to moving into a long term relationship. I was hurt really bad by my ex so I have built up a lot of walls around my heart and am trying to take them down in order to find the right person, however the process is slow and I need that special person to be patient with me as I will with them, while I take down the walls and start trusting again. I believe in being friends first, building a solid foundation of friendship and trust then creating a great relationship.

I like romance and being able to spoil a woman who is with me. I love to look into a woman's eyes for I believe they are the windows to her soul, you can learn a lot about a woman from her eyes. I like to be spontaneous, both adventure wise and romantically, you could come home and I have a rose petal path to the bedroom setup with candles and all ready for a relaxing massage, or a candlelight dinner for us to be together, or even a trip out maybe for a walk, or a ride to somewhere we can sit and snuggle and watch the stars, or even a movie, out or in, I will watch the romance "chick flicks" with you. As long as I can have you in my arms. and you don't mind me crying lol they get me emotional, and I'm not afraid to cry.

I am a true believer in everything happens for a reason and everyone we meet in life serves a purpose, we may not know right away what that reason or purpose is, but eventually it will show itself and many pieces of the life puzzle will fall into place.

I am not completely outgoing but I am ongoing.Nobody hates me but not everyone likes me. I'm not demanding and prefer the same. Im childlike at times but still responsible.

I am interested in nearly everything and would like to meet someone that shares at least some interests but also has their own. Someone with their own life who can add something to mine and vice versa.It would be good if they used a blinker when turning though. I can be a bit shy on a first meeting.I enjoy spending time away. Having a break recharges my batteries and fills me with joy and a renewed zest for life. I always seem to catch the happiness virus so be warned, I become highly contagious.
I am looking forward to the journey ahead but would prefer to travel through life with a compatible gentlewoman. I am ready to meet a great friend or companion at first which may lead to a permanent relationship but only if we are suited.
I am clean, well dressed, well groomed and subtly perfumed. I am honest, well mannered, kind and considerate with everyone and with those whom I love, I am very loyal, loving, affectionate & playful.
My friends consider me a handsome good catch. Heck, who am I to disagree with them?
One friend wrote to me saying,It is nice to know that you work for a cause not for applause
You live life to express not to impress,You don't strive to make your presence noticed.You just make your absence felt.We say you are a noble person which is a rare top find these days.

name: loufern
description:
I am divorced, single, no kids living with me. I spent most of my formative years in Europe, then moved to the USA. I am kinda new to the area. As a whole I am pretty easy-going, but am serious about the important things in life. Finding balance is key. Family is very important... then friends.. etc.
Love people, family, not a great sports lover, not a gym rat or mouse... or anything... I keep fit be being active. e.g. walking, hiking, tennis, swimming.. then chill Got a sense of humor. i.e.. sarcastic at times But mainly dry.. but a sense nonetheless!! 
Hmm, physical, mental / emotional health all good. Love the outdoors, staying active, love 2 travel, enjoy the arts, but can stay in too.I am not looking for you to make my life complete, whole etc.. I am looking for a great friend, partner... someone who wants to share their life with me and vice versa. To enjoy this journey together and make special memories to bind two hearts and souls. Anything else? Doggone.. you need more??? Just ask...
Oh, BTW.. divorced, just my shadow, great memories, wonderful dreams and the joy of life to keep me company.. 

Looking 4
The lady I am wanting to share life with, to spend time with must be honest, loyal, have a great sense of humor.. romantic, You will be smart, adventurous, love 2 travel, but equally happy staying home, drama free and able to balance the blended family needs.
You value our relationship but recognize the import of family, friendships. A relationship where love, kindness, mutual respect live. no thrive, where spontaneous conversation comes easy, with appreciation for each others individuality. As this is not our first rodeo, we all have "baggage. I buried mine, but I will dammed if it does try to make an appearance every now and again. However, the post office does not have a forwarding address.! So please be SINGLE and drama free.... 
We compliment and balance each other, and sensitive to each other's needs even if it's wants / desires that masquerade as needs i.e. romance! LOL 
Be my best friend, let's share our lives together. The rest will follow…
Well that’s about the gist of it...

description:
After an unhappy marriage and making sure my kids have been taken care of during the divorce, I now want to focus on myself a bit, and find someone to spend time with. Go for walks, hold hands, talk politics and economics, maybe technology (not mandatory), or just the wonderfully ridiculous magyarorszag. 

Igen, igen, elege jol beszelek magyarul (a billentyuzeten kivul) pedig nagyon szeretnek hogy te beszelsz angolul is mert allandoan beszelni magyarul faraszto, es neha jobban tudok mondani amit kell angolul.

My profile says not looking for anything serious, and that is mostly because I think looking for something serious is a fool's errand. Seriousness happens naturally, if it is to happen at all. I am not against falling back into a serious relationship but that is a journey, not a destination, however cheesey that sounds. 

Originally from Chicago, I became Hungarian in 2014, and have been living here on and off since 1990, with years spent back home and also in DC. 

I love reading, current events, traveling, cooking, and most of all being a good dad. Puzzles of any kind are fascinating, and I love most board games, trivia games at the pub are a favorite. I find anyone and everyone interesting, especially when they are telling me about their passions in life.

Musical tastes range from Zeppelin to Sinatra, Metallica to Rimsky-Korsakov, Amy Winehouse to NWA.

I have a BA in International Relations, an MEd in Educational Psychology. and an MS in Network Security.

Need any more details, let me know. They can be arranged. 

Cheers.

name: MykleMatwaya
description:
(StraightMale)
39, 5'10" 228lbs 
"I currently reside in the Los Angeles California area, however, I have come to the decision to permanently relocate to Mexico, somewhere in Baja Ca. I seek a better quality of life, slow down and enjoy humanity and give back to the people who need help. I would love to find someone wonderful to start to live this new life with

*No hook up's, no friends with benefits, or casual anythings. I appreciate the attention, compliments, & the offers. I'm very flattered, but it doesn't matter what you say, or how pretty you are, if you're not here for the same reason I am, please let's not waste each others time. I am just not into casual sex.

Hello & thank you for taking the time
to come here in order to satisfy your small curiosity in me.
I do hope that you find the information which I have placed here, to be both convenient, & useful to you in making up your mind as to whether or not you deem me worthy enough of any more of your valuable time. I do hope that you can both enjoy & appreciate what you find here about me, as I am very eager to begin to learn more & more about you. Thank you for your consideration, enjoy.

Im not a liar.
Im not a cheater.
Im not here for Sex.
Im not here for fun either.
My intentions are sound.

I have lived through enough to understand what the greatest things in life are truly made of, & they are not material, yet they do have substance. Among'st them are integrity, morality, modesty, & selflessness, to name a few. These are traits you cannot fake, you cannot buy them in the store or imitate them from watching television. They are gifts, God given & you either have them or you do not.

They do not give us much room to elaborate, so I will try to sum things up best I can. & while doing so, I promise to be honest with you. I am not going to make you spend the next few moments of your life listening to the same'ol tired routine of some @sswipe writing down everything he thinks you want to hear, fluffing himself up with attributes from a fairy tale & doing whatever else he can in order to blow enough smoke so far up your @ss that you start to think your panties must be on fire. Thats not me. Im not going to waste your time or mine by insulting your intellect. This is my 1st act towards you in order to gain your respect & trust, because those are the foundations of any lasting relationship, & thats what I am here to find. All I ask for in return, is that you appreciate this respectful courtesy which I am extending towards you, & that you please extend to me the same courtesy.

Now, before you read any further, the next fact that needs to be made abundantly clear is that I am nowhere close to perfect, not by anyone's standards. I am not wealthy (far from it) & I struggle through this life just like you & everyone else out there, if not more so. I am not skinny, or obese, nor am I the muscular & athletic type. I am however, a big, strong, healthy, loyal & very protective Alpha Male & Father. I am an honest person, understanding, patient & realistic. I am not controlling, abusive, or insecure, nor do I have a jealous bone in my body. I am highly emphatic & am ever aware & care very much about the effect I have on the people that are around me in any given place & at any given time. I am not thoughtless or insensitive. I detest rudeness & despise bullying of any kind, be it physical, intellectual, emotional, whatever, I wont have it & will not allow it to take place in my presence. I am a bit old-fashioned & I tend to romanticize the world, life & everything it has to offer, from the best of it, to the worst. To me it all has meaning & offers opportunity for learning & growth.
I do not believe in coincidences, accidents, chaos or chance, I believe in One God & I know he does not make mistakes, so therefore he would be contradicting himself if he were to allow them.

& If it's not crazy, mad, passionate, extraordinary love, then it is a waste of time. I have enough mediocre things in my life already & I refuse to allow love to be reduced down to just one more mediocrity.

I am in search of a woman who knows exactly whom she is. Someone who has struggled through her entire life, in order to be able to hold onto her true identity, her God given individuality, in order to be able to accept the person she sees staring back at her when ever she looks in a mirror. Who can accept herself for all that she is, both good & bad. Someone who accepts responsibility for her own actions & choices in life. Someone with empathy, patience & understanding. Morality, modesty & selflessness. Some one who loves for the sake of others & not merely for the sake of herself. I don't care what you have done,or haven't done (I haven't done much myself) I am no one of any particular importance, but I am one of a kind & that is pretty much all I am ever likely to be. I live my life by the examples which I set, based on the consistency of my character, & God willing, I will continue to do so until the day I die.
So, if your biggest fight has just been holding on to who you are, not what you have, then you & I already have something to relate to. I may not be much, but at least I am me, and I don't have to compromise my morality just to be able to blend in with everybody else out there.
All I want, all I have ever wanted all of my life, is for someone to treat me the same way I treat them. That may sound cliché, but it is true nonetheless. I am an easy man to please. The little things matter to me more than anything else, & I am a True Romantic in every sense of the word.
I am only looking for one girl, so if you read this & see yourself staring back from between these lines, then perhaps I have already found you.

I do not smoke, drink, or do drugs. That does not mean that I judge either. I just dont partake. I dont mind what you smoke, or if you drink. Everything best when done in moderation. But I will say this, I am not interested in compteing with any substances that a person chooses over & loves more than me or anything else in their life. But if you have a problem with something, that is not a dealbreaker either. Times are tough, & we are all hung up on something, in one way or another. Im here for you, & always will be.

I am not a sports fan, sorry. I just can't seem to be able to give a crap about any of them in any way whatsoever. (I remember a time when a woman would be relived to hear that.)
However, I can be talked into attending a game every so often, I just wont pay any attention to it.
If you have kid's that are on teams, I will be as supportive & as involved as I can be.
I enjoy literature & I like to do a little writing myself from time to time.
I am handy, & I prefer to fix things myself.
I Can't dance.
I like to cook & can cook.
Im a neat person & I tend to keep things tidy.
3 cat's may sound a bit excessive, but how many pairs of shoes do you own? They are very special to me & are a nice compliment to My lifestyle.
I'm not a selfish man, in bed or out.
I'm not impulsive & I don't jump to conclusions.

I am Muslim. For religion I put "other" & I only did that because 90% of you people stop reading right after you see "Muslim" in my personal details.
Hopefully by now, after all of this reading, you can see that I stand nowhere close to any negative stereotypes that you may have been conditioned into believing of us. I'm not some fanatic, chauvinist, controlling asshole, I wasn't raised that way. I am a rational, open minded non-judgemental individual. I am Muslim because of my own ability of subjective thought & by my own
choice. Not because of influence, heredity, or culture. No one talked me into this.This isn't just something I believe in, it is something I am convinced of.
I wasn't born into a Muslim lifestyle. I have no Muslim family members, or friends. That means, I am not doing this to impress mommy, daddy or anyone else.(Trust me, none of them like it one bit) This is for me, it is something dear to me, & it makes me feel better about you, myself, & everyone else out there. & so what if I pray 5x''s a day, & abstain from certain things that really aren't any good for me any ways? Whats the beef? At least I am a man who would rather follow rules & morality more than just his own selfish impulses, un-like most of the inconsiderate lil sh¡ts your used to dating. I am more focused, more disciplined, & a much better human being than I ever dreamed I could be. And being human is all I have every really wanted to be. And because of that,
I love being Muslim. It is the most important thing in the world to me.
But that does not mean that is has to be to you. Your beliefs are your own & mine are mine. I respect your choices & visa versa.

I would like to thank you coming this far. I tried my best to make all of this worth your time. Now after all of this,it is obvious that I am not lazy, nor do I lack the willingness to be considerate, expressive or informative I put my sincere effort into this, I am a pretty good writer when I want to be, but it does not happen easily. And even though I am capable of writing, & enjoy it very much, I will let you in on a little secret, none of that necessarily means that I am a great typist, or even a mediocre one. I am a terrible typist, & an even worse text'r. I spend so much time editing and with these tiny screens and bid thumbs it can be a real pain in the ass and is very frustrating...
That being said, I will text you a little, but please, not on & on. As you can probably tell by now I have a problem with summing things up, & making long stories short when I write. It's the same way when I text. I am very thorough & am not accustomed to leaving out important information when I communicate, information being the most important component to understanding. Therefore if you want to talk to me, then lets talk. Offer me the courtesy of a telephone call please. I have already put in so much time & effort with all of this writing, which is a'lot more than anyone else in here has been willing to do for you. So please be a sweetheart & give me a ring. name: Merl1970
description:
I’m an old fashioned man who loves to spoil the one he’s with. Opening the door isn’t something that is dead, and flowers aren’t just for Valentine’s Day or special occasions. Winning the heart of the woman you love doesn’t end with marriage, it’s an almost daily occurrence. I believe good manners and grammar still matter, even in texts. I try to live by the golden rule “treat others the way you want to be treated,” but I am not perfect. I love road trips and looking forward to travel around the country. I’m retired Navy and have been to 19 countries, and have plan on increasing that number. I have three grown children and three grandsons I just adore. So I’m looking forward to them being old enough to travel with me. 

I enjoy the quietness of living in the country. My town doesn’t even have a stop sign on the road going through it. I grew up in Detroit and was stationed in a few big cities. I just don’t like city living anymore. I’d describe myself as a pretty average guy. I’m only 5ft 8in, so I’m not too tall, definitely wish I was taller; I think that’s why I like my cowboy boots. I have three grown children and three grandsons I love to death. 

I’m looking for my best friend, confidant, and lover. Someone who I just enjoy being with no matter what we are doing. A person who just automatically glides next to me as we walk and we naturally just grab each other’s hand. My faith plays a part in my life, and would be a part of any relationship that I have. I enjoy going to church with the person I’m seeing. I’m Christian and go to a nondenominational church. I learned that having a similar basic belief structure just made for a stronger relationship. I’ve seen a lot of liberals say they want nothing to do with conservatives, so just to be forthcoming I am a conservative. Well that’s about it for now, I’ll add more as I think of it.

If you have only one picture, or only pictures with filters I probably won’t reply.

name: MasterMykeVaBch
occupation: semi retired, started a delivery service
description:
Hi there! My name is Myke. I live in Virginia Beach, VA. I am over 60. I am semi-retired. I own my own home and vehicle (lol so many women tell me about their guy friends living in their parent's basement, I figure this could be a bonus!) I am not your typical guy, I do have some...let's say "kinks and quirks" that you can get to know as we get to know each other better. I like to watch crime tv shows, listen to popular music, I am a comics fan, and enjoy watching movies too. I work part time doing deliveries to keep myself busy, and love gardening too. I have a prize rose bush in my front yard with a koi pond for quieter moments. I am a scorpio, my favorite season is fall, my favorite color is pink. 

I am looking for a woman, to date in person, and get to know, so that eventually I can continue to grow with someone on this fascinating journey thru life. I am ultimately seeking a lovely lady between 30-40 (give or take roughly) that I can create a family with, as I have had my time of success in business, and want to slow down (a bit..not entirely as I have a lot to still offer to the world!) and smell more of the roses. 

What are my preferences? Everyone has them, and no one should be critiqued for them. I love women of all sizes and shapes but as I have had a few car accidents and surgeries along the journey, I believe I can be a better lover to a petite to medium sized woman. Don't get me wrong, I love thick women...but I am not sure how I will handle one now in more intimate moments and positions. You will find that I am very upfront and honest, as I don't want to waste anyone's time. Life is too short to do that. That being said, if you are a scammer...please just skip me and move on to your next target. I have probably already talked to you and smoked you out by now. LOL If you are a genuine person however...keep reading.
I DO have a "thing" for exotic women...latin women...island women...love a strong woman who can hold her own in life but knows who her heart and soul belongs with and to at home. I also enjoy a woman who likes women as well. I am open to a poly relationship, but I am seeking my primary first and foremost. If a second never arrives, it will not matter to me, as I have been there and done that...could most definitely write a book about it! Would probably sell better than 50 Shades of Grey...for all the same reasons lol not to mention...that was romance drivel. As far as that goes, I have been a part of the BDSM community for more than 40 years. I have managed a poly family of more than 5, and earned the title Master with them. Although I still ache for those moments at times, I have settled a bit with time, and now see myself as a Dom more than a Master. Master is a term that I can still use, but only with one that deserves to utilize it. I am definitely not a member of the Ddlg community, but I understand and respect it. One of my very best friends is heavily involved in that community, and should we decide to progress...you will be vetted by her. I trust her implicitly. Everyone should have friends that can help them see a bigger picture, and be an objective assistant that will help your life grow. We are very close as only platonic friends, she lives with me with her two young daughters, so you can ask her about how I am with kids! She is a S/switch but I am seeking someone clearly submissive. 

Do I want kids? Yes. Kids of my own. At least one. That is the one job I have always wanted but never got. So if that is not something you want in the future, I wish you the best. 

Why am I not taken and on a dating website? Great question! I was married...and she decided to follow down a different path that no longer included me, or men. So, I am back on the market! I will also be honest that the divorce is not final, but I have no interest and neither does she in going back to being married together. We are clearly looking for different things in life at this point.

If you are still reading, it can't hurt to reach out and at least make a new friend. We can all use more of those. There has to be some interest at this point right? I look forward to hearing from you!

In no particular order, I love cooking, working out, trying new foods, beautiful scenery, art, music, movies (action-adventure, sci-fi, and chick flicks), talking on a variety of subjects, sunrises in summer, sunsets all year, waking up when I feel ready, brainstorming, dreaming and planning, holding hands (yes, in public), hugs and kisses (and sex).

I discuss instead of arguing. You're entitled to your feelings and your perspective. I'm sensitive and intuitive... no drama or conflict. I enjoy time alone, but not to the point of being lonely. I prefer to be with someone most of the time.

I love my critters (2 dogs, 2 cats). I love being retired.

I'm direct and don't play games. If you want to know something, ask -- I don't bite. I like to laugh, but not at the expense of others.

I'm a toucher, hugger, and snuggler. I'm looking for the same in a man. I'm here for a friend, lover, and true partner. I'm here for someone who wants the long-haul, not a fling. I'm here for the love of my life for the rest of my life.

Let’s laugh together and we’re half way there!
Hiya... my name’s George, thanks for stopping by.... so time for me to rabbit on about myself... Im young at heart down to earth, honest (maybe too honest) easy going and have a heart of gold...
I believe that mutual respect & trust are crucial to the success of any relationship...
One of the things I look forward to is going on holiday, nothing better than being with the woman you love, lazing on the beach, drink in hand and the sun shining.
I like science fiction and action films the most but also enjoy a good romantic film as well (sob… sob…) I listen to all sorts of music… soul... rock... pop... etc
I’m not into any sports, but I do enjoy watching F1...
I enjoy going out to the movies, 10 pin bowling having meals out at restaurant going for walks in the country side… I also enjoy staying in at home and having a cosy evening… I’m open minded and willing to try almost anything at least once!
I’ve been in a couple of relationships since my divorce the most recent one ended recently after a number of broken promises. 
My main career has been in sale’s management but gave it up about after being made redundant three times in as many years, I’m now semi retired and only work part time... it keeps me out of mischief... lol
to sum myself up in a sentence I would say 'Bubbly, good fun, honest, generous & most importantly I love to laugh...
So.... what am I looking for? Well, it’s YOU!.. YES... YOU... get in touch and we’ll take it from there... you’ve got nothing to lose and everything to gain... I don’t bite... well, not unless you ask... lol
Well, enough about me... so... “How are you” ??

name: benjden
description:
3rd Party Descriptive Analysis Personality Report

Ben has a strong need to belong, and the organizations or groups he chooses are lucky to attract this thoughtful, hardworking, and devoted individual. Ben focuses all his energy on the problems or issues that is before him at the moment; he is painstakingly accurate when working with facts, attentive to details, and methodical in applying both qualities while working. Ben likes gatherings, analyzing, and applying data for some useful purpose, and documenting the results.

Quiet and reserved, Ben is a loyal and devoted friend and co-worker who takes his responsibilities toward others very seriously. Sensitive and sympathetic, Ben is a good listener, eager to help people in real and practical ways, which Ben does best by drawing on his own personal experiences. he is also good with people in small groups or one-on-one situations because of his patience and genuinely sympathetic approach to dealing with people. Ben makes a pleasant and reliable co-worker and exemplary employee, but tends to be harried and uncomfortable in supervisory roles. 

Love and Relationships
Ben has a few, close friends, and is extremely loyal to these, and is ready to provide emotional and practical support at a moment's notice. The older the friendship is, the more Ben will value it. 

Ben is devoted to partners and friends (no family) and usually is an excellent homemaker. His home of is likely to be well kept inside and out. Interior and exterior are meticulously maintained and appointed in the traditional manner. Ben is apt to find the putting on the airs of offensive and tends to prefer modest, quiet friends, rather than more boisterous ones.

As the security seeking temperament, Ben is a practical and frugal type, who shares certain core values, among them the belief in a strong work ethic, the need for people and institutions to be responsible, the importance of following the rules and of serving one's community.

• Introversion
While Ben may not be anti-social, he does need his private time & space to retreat from the world. Unlike extroverts, too much socializing may zap his energies, which are derived from exploring the inner world of ideas, impressions and pure thought.

• Sensing
Ben usually gathers information with his senses: what he can see, hear, taste, touch and smell in the physical world. Ben concentrates his energies on what actually exists and does not ponder what might exist too much. He is usually practical and relies on his common sense to guide him through the world. 

• Feeling
Ben makes decisions subjectively based upon his values and what is important to him. How people will be affected by his decisions is important to him. He is likely to make decisions based upon what he feels is acceptable and agreeable rather than what is logical. His truths are founded in his values and those of the society he lives in.

• Judgement
He likes decisions to be made as soon as possible; he is not comfortable with loose ends and like to see conflicts resolved as soon as possible; he has a preference for a well-structured, orderly lifestyle with few surprises. Ben takes commitments very seriously. While he is not inflexible, he does like to stick to a plan once it is set into motion..

I have employed an analyst’s 3rd Party Vivid Analysis Personality Report , but there is little space for me to provide this assessment here. So, if interested please contact for the balance of this section.

name: GaryF
description:
I truly enjoy the company and companionship of a woman. If we can sit alone for hours and be captivated by just talking and watching each other, then it is real! Yes, I am a hopeful romantic who needs affection - receiving and giving. 

I am attracted to intelligence and humor and also sensual women who have a good understanding of who they are and what they want out of life, and have ease in communicating their feelings, wants, desires, and fears. Keywords: Intriguing, alluring, smoldering, funny, kind, honest. I am well-traveled and plan to continue. 

I enjoy all art forms and am also an artist in multiple mediums. I currently make my living as a Chief Marketing Officer and also as film producer-director, within the high technology entertainment marketing arenas. I am well read and also have a highly developed sense of street smarts (Boston NYC). 

So yes, I am opinionated, passionate about everything I do, and understand loyalty and integrity. Laughing is critical, and maintaining a healthy balance daily is also important to me. I do not engage in the single' bar scene, juggle relationships, or tolerate dishonesty--life is too short, and time is too precious. I love people and work hard to maintain relationships with those I care about. Family and friends are near and dear to me. My Parents were married for 63 years!! 

My perfect dream scenario: Austin and a villa in Tuscany close to Firenze, a wife who I adore and makes me weak just at the thought of her. Family, friends, music, art, debate, discussion, good food, wine. I would have my studio close by, writing and directing the script swirling in my head and filming across Europe. My wife will be my closest friend, and my family is my greatest treasure. My Mother is my best friend, and my son means more to me than words can describe. 

Hmm, who am I seeking? You have your life on track - does not have to be perfect but it should be moving. You take care of yourself. You allure me (I allure you). You are not too scarred from past relationships (remember: I am not him). You are motivated and curious about learning and discovering. You are a happy person and you like people. Romance, playfulness, seduction and intrigue sprinkled with adventure are our favorite pastimes and applied to everything...even the mundane. You have goals and hopefully I am one of them! 

You are moved by the small things and little considerations. You are active and physical. You're a comfortable chameleon in diverse social situations, but probably prefer jeans and a t-shirt and down time too. Have I mentioned feminine, nurturing, passionate and sensual? I've got the masculine side covered, not looking for any additional traits there. 

You adore my son who is 17 years old as of this writing, and he adores you (I am not looking for a substitute mother, but you MUST possess those critical values). I believe in soul mates, I believe in love at first site, and hopefully life has not taken these romantic notions from you. As I said earlier in this profile, I know who I am, and I've spent the time and energy looking inward to be in a place of personal peace. I am also fully aware that finding yourself is the first step in finding true companionship along with patience and an appreciation of timing! 

So, as I stuff this letter into the bottle and cast it out to sea, to whomever finds this; know I do not need to be rescued - just someone to share the island with!! If you have gotten this far are you Her? 

- I realize that some people use this site to socialize and as a means to meet and correspond with many people. For clarity, I have no desire to swap emails for extended periods of time. I am interested in expressing mutual interest in each other and meeting in person to see if there is actual attraction and genuine chemistry. Lastly, I am what I describe above, and look like my photos, please be the same. In short: Nice Guy looking to meet Nice Girl...fall deeply in love - Simple Right?

name: juanheredia
description: Nací en Mendoza Argentina, crecí en una familia común, 4 hermanos así me forme DE TRATO SIMPLE, me fui haciendo de apoco SIMPATICO, Estudie, primario secundario y Universidad y me hice muy SOCIABLE. Conocí un insólito e inquebrantable grupo de amigos y sutilmente me integré a la simple actitud de ser SOLIDARIO. Experimente el trabajo profundo de verme a mi mismo junto con mis amigos de sentimiento humanista por lo que me voy transformando día a día en NO VIOLENTO, con mi juventud y madures transito en la asombrosa actividad social, solidaria y no violenta advierto que con todo ello que soy indeleblemente ALEGRE, eso me hizo darme cuenta que tenia que vivir TRANQUILO, no obstante, me revelé de apoco que tenía que ser en todos los ámbitos un hombre PENSANTE, y en todo lo que expreso en mis actividades me distingo por ser muy EFUSIVO. Me apareje varias veces naciendo de ellas 2 hijas, así vislumbré que soy SEDUCTOR, Luego los amores que se deslizan, en mis noches de bohemia, me denuncian que soy un arquetipo VIRIL, Vivo actualmente solo y me manifiesto con la rutina del conocimiento que me demuestra ser ALGO SOLITARIO. Así la posibilidad de una concluyente pareja y el tiempo quizás dejen que renazca en mi pensamiento la idea de dejar de ser A VECES ALGO ERMITAÑO….Para unirme A UNA GRAN MUJER que pueda cerrar el libro de mis días junto a ella.. Por eso a ella LE DIGO, a la que me quiera acompañarme con la belleza de su ser. Una de mis aspiraciones es: Siente el calor del sol, mira el brillo de la luna, y respira el aire de la montaña, ASÍ con el más profundo de tu deseo, imaginarás lo que és “El amor perfecto”. Luego, cuando leyendo libros no encuentres tu búsqueda… Sé que Pensarás en el aroma de néctares olvidados en el mundo de los recuerdos,,, Sentirás la noche mas bella,,, y SI en mi regazo, anhelas tu último amanecer, Sabrás leer en mis ojos “El sentido del Amor”. Solo exprésame que,, JAMÁS EN LA VIDA DEJARÁS DE BUSCARME,,,, Haaa!!!! Y de ningún modo olvides... El pretexto más necio es culpar al destino.-

name: trancetrousers
description:
I'm just a nice normal man looking for a nice normal woman. I’m fairly young at heart - I can be playful and silly at times but I also know when to be serious and grown up. I work full time, I can drive and I have a car. I also have a 9 year old daughter who is obviously my main priority. She doesn't live with me but I see her regularly, so if you can't accept this or think it might be a problem then you should look elsewhere. I do still have plenty of free time though!

I like the simple things in life e.g. days out, country/seaside walks, quiet nights in, the odd trip to the cinema etc. In the summer I like to go for rides on my mountain bike when I can. I have social anxiety so I don't really like pubs much unless they're really quiet ones, and definitely not clubs! I'm an animal lover, I have a dry sense of humour and I like a good laugh. I'm a very tactile person and love kissing, cuddling or just holding hands. I'm also polite, courteous and fully house trained, oh, and I always leave the toilet seat down! I'm reliable, honest and trustworthy. My motto in life is treat others as you'd like to be treated yourself.

I’m quite a neat and tidy person. One of my pet hates is poor spelling and grammar. I’m not really interested in sport. My main hobby is building models - plastic, metal and card.

You'll probably be about my age, although obviously I wouldn’t say no to anyone who wasn’t if they ticked all the right boxes. I have no problem with age gap relationships, so if you’re a lot younger than me then that’s fine. If you’re child free and you want to get in touch then you must like children, but if you have children already you’re also welcome to contact me, particularly if you’re a yummy mummy lol.

With any luck you'll be reasonably attractive, with all your own hair and teeth lol, and hopefully agree with most, if not all, of what I’ve written about myself above. I'm just looking for a like minded person really. If you like trance music and/or Star Trek/Star Wars too then that would be great! It would be good if you had a car too.

description:
I am someone how just come out from a long term relationship, I was truly invested into it but things did not turn out to plan so here I am. Not sure what I am looking for but one thing is sure is that I want to meet new people as friends or more and see where it can lead.

I am a very positive person, very focused in what I do and when its time to work its time to work, when it is time to laugh and enjoy then we enjoy. I like outdoor activities but also enjoy the comfort of a sofa or bed to enjoy watching a nice movie with the right person next to me. 

I originally come from Mauritius island, lived 8 years in the UK and soon to be 3 years in Spain. I moved a lot meaning that I am of mix culture and very adaptive, now my goal is to integrate fully into the Spanish culture. To me Spain is a beautiful country full of opportunities for everyone.

I am full of stories and little life lessons due to my highly active life and experiences. I am looking for someone how is mature enough to have deep conversations around a glass of wine, someone who has a certain level of spiritual awakening and who is willing to grow to make the most of this life journey. 

If you match these characteristics then maybe I will share with you some of my near-death experiences and crazy stories. 

My job now as Motorcycle racing coach, I also do fitness, meditation, wellbeing, and scuba diving activities. I am myself an ex European Championship winner which allowed me the possibility to work in my passion freely. I am an entrepreneur currently building my business in Spain which gives me a lot of freedom of choice.

Looking for someone cool, kind and trustworthy to make friends hang out with and see what happens. No need to rush in to anything but I am not looking to just hook up either. I am not looking for someone to text forever and I don't need to go to another place to message like hangouts or WhatsApp Right here is fine until we exchchange phone numbers or whatever. Nobody has a working phone on dating sites for talking or video chat ? Amazing! If your profile picture is someone besides you (amature porn star or Instagram model) please don't contact me. I am also not willing to do a long distance relationship with someone that is an unreasonable distance away a few hours is fine but across the country or overseas I am not doing that .
I work for myself and I am single, never married with no kids. I have a very dark sense of humor and think being cynical is funny which gives the impression I have a negative attitude which could not be further from the truth I think I am hilarious. Is that wrong? I do not like negative people or people who have anger management issues. There is never a reason to behave in such negative ways and I immediately separate myself from those type of people I am an animal lover especially dogs, 
I like pizza, nachos, motorcycles rock and roll especially ounk rock , old cars, road trips and the outdoors, I am a life long vegetarian and I don't care if anyone else is or isn't one.

name: littlemansmom
description:
I like to think of myself as a pretty fun person, when given the chance. Loyalty is a trait I not only possess, but admire in others. If you are lucky enough to find yourself in my inner circle, I will move mountains to keep you there. Honesty is another trait I look for in others, and therefore I shall be as upfront about myself as possible here. I am no supermodel, for sure...but I think I could probably still turn some heads...then again, you never know. (Self-deprecating humor is also something I am VERY good at) I am not the skinniest, nor the heaviest girl you'll ever meet...just somewhere nicely in between. Some say that just means more to love, eh?? I love my crazy family, and I have an 8 year old son who is my everything. I lost my husband three years ago and just recently decided it might be okay to have some fun again. My son occupies a great deal of my time, so I'm still just trying to figure out how all of this would work, but I'm willing to give it a shot. So, if you are willing to take a chance, send me a line sometime...and don't be afraid to be funny...funny is good...very good. 

P.S. – I have already been scammed twice by so-called “Military Men”. So, I am now quite wary of this whole process....and on the lookout for anything that just doesn't quite make sense. I hate how doubtful I have been made to feel, but I suppose that it just how it goes in this day and age.

name: Kamaainagal
description:
I am looking for my best friend. The person I can’t wait to come home to and find out how his day was and tell him about mine. 
A person that we can enjoy making dinner or breakfast and just teasing each other and laughing. That on a rainy day, we can sit outside listen to the rain and enjoy just being together cuddling.
When I think of him, it makes my heart smile. If I look across the room and I can wink or smile and he will know I am blessed and thankful he is in my life and we are doing this together. As partners. Not a leader or a follower.
A person who accepts my faults and loves me more for them. Not erates or tries to change me.


I have 2 great danes that are therapy animals. We volunteer at the VA hospitals’ Psych ward, Dimentia and Long term care units.
We also volunteer at the children’s hospital and with kids with special needs.

I believe in giving back to our community and it’s my way of honoring god.

I’ve recently moved to Nashville. I am learning that I enjoy country music. I am discovering my faith again. While I don’t necessarily attend church. I do believe in a higher power. And that he has a plan for each of us. 

I love to cook. It’s my way of decompressing. I enjoy a cocktail and chatting with the person who has captured my heart, while we make dinner together. I love waking up, and seeing him still asleep. Makes my heart smile and is a blessing that I would count each and every morning.

I want him to know that I will stand beside him. For him when he needs me. I will protect his heart, because it’s a precious gift that he chose to give. I want him to never worry about what will happen with us. Because I will give my all to making our relationship last a life time. As I would expect the same.

I am 1000% honest. And sometimes that gets me in trouble. Because you will not like some answers. But I will Never lie. 

I love to go to the beach, for walks in nature, for a drive, and just enjoying the company of the person I am with. Not necessarily conversing the entire time. But just enjoy being together.

name: ParadiseBill
description:
Instead of you trying to figure out what I am all about, I'll just say it here so you can be the judge as to if you would like to message me. Fair enough?
I'm 57yr 5'8 215lb bald head and active male. I own a swimming pool company that I currently work just part time now because I can. Here is the bad part (lets get it over with, haha) Been married 3 times. 1st time I was too young (18) and had 2 children. Both are grown and gone. 2nd one was only interested in her own family, not just to say hello. Spent days off there as well as financial help for them. 3rd one I am separated from. She lives in another state so it is just me and my 2 dogs for company. I've been separated for over 3 years and have just now decided to take a chance for romance. I believe I am old enough and wise enough now to know exactly what I am looking for. Also to say this up front, I am not looking for sex. What I am looking for is sincerity like wanting to hold hands or just a simple kiss without me having to ask. I don't want to be a home body and do nothing. Perhaps dinner, movies or anything really to get out and enjoy. I am not much for traveling, sorry. I have a slight phobia about closed in areas like planes. I don't like to be around a lot of people, meaning about 25 or more. I am more of a secluded person when we would go out. I think it is because I like my private life and don't want it to be public. Like I said, after over 3 years, I've decided to come out of my shell and hope for a real person with real intentions toward me. I consider myself a really fun guy to be around and sometimes goofy just to make you smile. I do have manners and always know how to treat women appropriately so they will always be glad to be with me. I hope this might give you an insight to my life and hopes. If you find this rather nice and pleasant for a change then message me and let's see if we can connect! Until then, take care and have a great life!

name: jfcj
description:
Jfcj lleva 25 años componiendo música para televisión, publicidad, documentales y exposiciones. Realizó sus estudios musicales en los conservatorios de Oviedo y Madrid. Después de terminar estos estudios se presentó a oposiciones después de superarlas trabajó como profesor en conservatorio durante 20 años, donde combinó su actividad docente con la dirección de una empresa propia dedicada a la producción de contenidos para el sector audiovisual.
La música que escribe está especialmente diseñada para producciones audiovisuales y videojuegos. Algunas de estas composiciones son melódicas, pero otras carecen de esta característica porque han sido diseñadas como un acompañamiento para sensaciones, actividades o estados de ánimo.
Utiliza instrumentos musicales convencionales que pertenecen a una partitura orquestal. Algunos de ellos son electrónicos y recrean sonidos analógicos y digitales que realmente le gusta escuchar. Tiene debilidad por la música europea antigua y tradicional, estilos que grabó y tocó durante muchos años con algunos conjuntos musicales, por lo que de vez en cuando publica melodías basadas en repertorios medievales o renacentistas. Por lo general, trata de darles un procesamiento adecuado sin aspiraciones históricas, algo esencial para su correcto funcionamiento en productos audiovisuales.

name: antoinjaajaa
description:
I follow my words and I'm a man of my words.I'm single never married. I'm seeking for a long term relationship that could lead to marriage. I'm cleansed with my own tears for true love, so I will remain pure for evermore. Only great joy or great sorrow can reveal my truth. I look up high to see only the light, and never look down to see my shadow. By true love, I could live on the fragrance of the earth, and like an air plant be sustained by the light. 
I have a strong personality. I'm self confident, strong willed, romantic, sensual, independent, honest, sincere, upright, patient, persistent, very bold, refined, talented, corageous, valiant, manifold and many sided... I'm very educated and well mannered. I always develop myself and I treat others the way I want them to treat me. I will stay clean, upright, transparent, charitable, and fair to the oppressed, but hard on people oppressors. I'm always patient in pain, strong and above all lowly passions... But I always say: Save me, God, from myself, cleanse me of all my impurities. Forge me in the forge of Your Right...
Otherwise, I'm very fond of music and dance, because dancing give me the chance to express my emotions, and it arouses different feelings in my soul. So I'm very calm in my life, but very crazy in my love. 
I adore Love and Beauty because they are the reflection of God in me. I want to live by kindness which should be the source of every law upon the earth, for kindness is the shadow of God in me. To me, the true great love makes miracles and heals from diseases. It is boundless and has no age. Effectively, I prefer death through happiness of love a thousandfold to life in vain and despair. I prefer to be a dreamer among modest and poor men, than being a rich man among those who are without dreams and desires...
Moreover, by love, my second nature can transform me in one new person. So I must be devoted to love and life, because, what I get out of it depends of what I put into it...
And all my life, I've been searching for the true love, for a face, for a look... I'm perpetually in a state of wandering... searching... my future beloved... It's so easy to find a person to live with, but it's so hard to find the one without whom I can't live.

I teach math and art. I love my job. I am a country girl at heart. I like to spend most of my summer at the river. I like to swim, fish, float, camp, bon fires,  drink a few, listen to music, hang with family and friends, etc. I also like dancing in the rain and jumping in mud puddles! Lol!

I am looking to date until meet a decent man that I click with and want to pursue something more. Ultimately, I am looking for a lifetime romance. I want a man that has it all! I am looking for intelligence, passionate, romantic, compassionate, sympathetic, humorous, affectionate, good work ethic, has goals, a god in the sack, smokin' hot looks doesn't hurt but not a requirement lol! Someone who will go out of his way to do the little things in life to make me feel loved and desired. Someone who is my best friend and partner.
That being said, I know that things don't happen overnight, and I am NOT willing to rush into anything. Friendship is always a great start!
